law.text:
The Secretary may:
Conduct research to determine ginseng population trends, propagation techniques or ways of conserving ginseng;
Promote the conservation and export of ginseng;
Establish standards for the certification of ginseng intended for export;
Establish guidelines and requirements for the conservation and harvesting of ginseng;
Require that records be kept by any person who harvests or buys ginseng intended for sale; and
Establish conditions under which a permit or registration may be suspended or revoked.
